</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【實試】MSI Sword 15 入門級電競手提電腦　 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 植入</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/11/msi-sword-15/review-2/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=msi-sword-15</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[小白]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 11 Nov 2021 09:25:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[MSI]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sword 15]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1070207</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>想選購一款有一定打機能力的手提電腦，電競手提電腦是不二之選，既毋須「食炒」買顯示卡，也有一定的流動性，但大多數 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>想選購一款有一定打機能力的手提電腦，電競手提電腦是不二之選，既毋須「食炒」買顯示卡，也有一定的流動性，但大多數電競手提電腦定價不菲，要擁有就要付出不少金錢。究竟電競手提電腦是否就一定是貴價款？MSI Sword 15 正是一款配備 11 代 Core 處理器及內置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 顯示卡但定價不到$10,000 的電競手提電腦，MSI Sword 15 有什麼賣點？效能又如何？以下筆者就為大家進行實試。</p><h2>擅長插畫名人操刀設計</h2><p>筆者之前實試過多款電競手提電腦均以暗調示人，配以燈光整體外觀的確是相當型格，不過其實並非只有黑暗系用色才夠酷，白色也可顯出型格一面。MSI Sword 15 就正是以白色為主調，配以黑色屏幕邊框及機底，造出強烈對比，而且 MSI 找來曾為《三國志》、《信長之野望》等遊戲製作封面插畫的長野剛（NAGANO TSUYOSHI）為 MSI Sword 15 打造出專為玩家而設計的產品與視覺創意，機身的線條融入武士刀感覺，加上機身其他細位以及標誌性、以浮雕方式刻印於機面的 MSI 龍魂 Logo，MSI Sword 15 整機外觀其實不下於高階的電競手提電腦。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_02.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070217" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_02.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI Sword 15 以白色為主調，配以黑色屏幕邊框及機底，造出強烈對比。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_05.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070220" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_05-694x392.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_05-694x392.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_05-768x434.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_05.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI 標誌性的龍紋 Logo 為浮雕方式刻印於機面。</p><h2><strong>仍備有 USB 2.0 </strong><strong>介面</strong></h2><p>一向 MSI 的電競手提電腦都有不錯的介面配置，而 Sword 15 的 I/O 數量與布局算是中規中矩。機身左邊備有兩個 USB-A，其中一個為 USB 2.0 規格；至於右邊則備有一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A 介面、一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-C、HDMI 及 LAN 介面，當然亦有耳機 / 咪高峰插孔。始終是較為平價的電競手提電腦，因此未有配備 Thunderbolt 4 介面是可以理解，但三個 USB-A 介面中有一個 USB 2.0 規格，雖說可以用來接駁其他較低速度的裝置，但如果轉為 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A，令 Sword 15 的 USB-A「清一色」同一規格會較好。要留意，機身上的 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-C 是不支援 PD 充電功能，外出時記得一定要帶火牛。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_06.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070221" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_06-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_06-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_06-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_06.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機身左邊備有兩個 USB-A，其中一個為 USB 2.0 規格。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_07.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070222" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_07-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_07-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_07-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_07.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲右邊則備有一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-A 介面、一個 USB 3.2 Gen2 的 USB-C、HDMI 及 LAN 介面，當然亦有耳機 / 咪高峰插孔。</p><h2>100% 鍵盤植入並具備 Num Pad 設計</h2><p style="text-align: left;">以往多款高階的 MSI 手提電腦也配備 SteelSeries 鍵盤，今回 Sword 15 因為定價較低的關係，僅配備藍色背光鍵盤。不過此鍵盤具備 1.7mm 鍵程，實際輸入手感尚算不錯，而且是 100% 鍵盤，具備 Num Pad 設計，加上多個快速鍵，一般使用以及打機時的體驗令人滿意。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_03.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070218" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_03-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_03-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_03-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_03.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲估計為定價較低的關係，僅配備藍色背光鍵盤，屬 100% 鍵盤設計。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_04.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070219" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_04-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_04-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_04.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲具備 Num Pad 及多個快速鍵，1.7mm 鍵程下實際輸入手感尚算不錯。</p><h2><strong>GeForce RTX 3050 Ti </strong><strong>獨立顯示卡搭配 Intel </strong><strong>第 11 </strong><strong>代 Core i5 </strong><strong>處理器</strong></h2><p>MSI Sword 15 搭載了第 11 代 Intel Core i5-11400H 處理器，為 11 代 Intel Core i5 中具性價比的型號，屬 6 核心規格，以及內置 GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 獨立顯示卡，並具備 4GB GDDR6 記憶體。雖然 Intel Core i5-11400H 處理器的 TDP 為 45W，但為了處理器與 GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 在全速運行下不會因熱力使效能下降，廠方於 Sword 15 機體內置 Cooler Boost 5 散熱模組，以雙風扇達致高氣流量，配合最多 6 組散熱管，確保機內廢熱可即時排走。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_09.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070224" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_09-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_09-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_09-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_09.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機體內置 Cooler Boost 5 散熱模組，廢熱由機身後方及側邊排出。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_10.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070225" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_10.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲機底的六角形大型入風口設計特別，亦可見 Cooler Boost 5 散熱模組具備多條散熱管。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_14.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070229" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_14-694x543.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="543" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_14-694x543.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_14-768x600.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_14.jpg 921w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可使用 3D 環繞 Nahimic 遊戲音效。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_12.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070227" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_12-694x423.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="423" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_12-694x423.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_12-768x469.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_12.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新設計的 MSI Center 收藏所有專屬功能，將監控、調整與最佳化等多種實用功能都整合為一。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_16.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070231" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_16-694x394.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_16-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_16-768x436.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_16.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲MSI App Player 使用戶可在 Sword 15 上遊玩不同 Andorid 遊戲，帶來另類手遊體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_20.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070235" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_20-621x580.jpg" alt="" width="621" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_20-621x580.jpg 621w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_20-768x717.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_20.jpg 771w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 621px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲搭載第 11 代 Intel Core i5-11400H 處理器。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070232" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17-694x519.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17-1204x900.jpg 1204w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17-768x574.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_17.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲配備 16GB RAM 下，PCMark 得分為 6085 分。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_18.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070233" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_18-694x375.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="375" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_18-694x375.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_18-768x415.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_18.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲內置 NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 獨立顯示卡，3DMark Time Spy 得分為 5498 分，效能相當不錯，有 RTX 3060 過大半的水準。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_19.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070234" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_19-694x434.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="434" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_19-694x434.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_19-768x480.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_19.jpg 1152w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲利用 CrystalDiskMark 測試 512GB 的 SSD 硬碟，讀取部份達 1986.39MB/s 而寫入部份則達 980.21MB/s ，速度普普通通。</p><h2><strong>具備 IPS-Level 144Hz </strong><strong>屏幕</strong></h2><p>說到打機體驗，Sword 15 除了配備，另一樣重要就是屏幕。Sword 15 使用了 FHD 解像度的 IPS-Level 屏幕，可達 144Hz 更新率。實測這個屏幕流暢度相當不錯，平時睇片的效果亦交足功課，亮度與對比度令筆者滿意，Anti-Glare 設計在文書處理環境時會有更舒適的觀看體驗。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_11.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1070226" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/MSI-Sword-15_11.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲15.6 吋 IPS-Level 屏幕質素是不錯的，亮度與對比度令筆者滿意。</p><h2>總結：</h2><p>配備第 11 代 Intel Core i5-11400H 處理器、內置 GeForce RTX 3050 Ti 獨立顯示卡，亦有 144Hz IPS-Level 屏幕及支援 192KHz / 24bit HI-RES Audio，MSI Sword 15 以 $9,799 的定價來說，是相當吸引的一款電競手提電腦。Sword 15 推出時更會免費升級至 Windows 11，讓用戶即時體驗最新 Windows 作業系統帶來的新功能。</p><p>另外，現時 MSI 官方網站亦有 Black Friday 優惠，即日起至 11 月 28 日購買 MSI 指定筆電享有折扣，最多減 HK$2,500，更加碼贈送滑鼠、耳機、電腦包。有興趣了解或購買可<a href="https://hkstore.msi.com/pages/2021-promo-black-friday">按此</a>。</p></p><div class="feedflare">
